@timoncc @albpalau @SylTilt I did the following to estimate. You can do s/1000/1/ to get a full count.

var tot = 0;
for (var i = 0; i &lt; 6000000; i += 1000) {
    tot += eth.getBlock(i).size * 1000;
    console.log(i, tot);
}

The estimate gave 50 GB.

